FDRIVER_OLD DIRECTORY -- Zoltan F90 test driver application source code.
------------------------------------------------------------------------
NOTE:  This directory contains the old version of the fdriver, using Zoltan's
LB_* interface names.  It is maintained for testing the backward-compatability
of Zoltan with older applications.  New fdriver development should be done in
the "fdriver" directory.

